## Limitations

The findings are based on available data and surveys, which may not capture the full spectrum of voter preferences. Additionally, the data is subject to change as new surveys are conducted and as political landscapes evolve. The analysis is also limited by the availability of recent studies and the potential biases inherent in survey methodologies.